# Agent Skills — IDE Rules

## MANDATORY
1. ALL subagent calls MUST route through SKILLS_ROUTER.md
2. NEVER skip pre-flight check before Gemini CLI calls
3. ALWAYS use timeout for subagent calls (max 120s)
4. ALWAYS clean output boilerplate before presenting
5. ALWAYS credit source: "According to Gemini subagent: ..."

## ROUTING
Read SKILLS_ROUTER.md at conversation start.
Match tasks against trigger conditions. Load skills ONLY when triggered.

## ERROR HANDLING
- command not found → install instructions
- 429 rate limit → wait 30-60s, max 2 retries
- timeout → simplify prompt
